name: Jodie Comer
description:
Textual Inversion of Jodie Comer

I'm back from my holidays with this new TI. On the airplane I saw her in Free Guy so I thought why not bring her to SD. Works well in a lot of different models but it helps to put necklace, hair clip or earrings in the negative to keep control of the accessories.

Trigger word is jodiecomer_TI

v1 was trained with 14 images for 2300 steps
